better decisions.

00:13:47.620 --> 00:13:49.105
And I think that adds
a lot of value.

00:13:49.105 --> 00:13:49.880
NAZMUL IDRIS: That true.

00:13:49.880 --> 00:13:53.830
The social proof is a really,
really big component of

00:13:53.830 --> 00:13:56.500
actually enhancing my
experience, because if I'm

00:13:56.500 --> 00:13:59.640
looking for a particular
application in Google Play,

00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:01.190
and Sam has +1'ed it.

00:14:01.190 --> 00:14:03.100
I trust Sam, Sam is awesome.

00:14:03.100 --> 00:14:06.660
So then by extension, I think
